Class Maybe<A>

  • java.lang.Object
    • drjoliv.jfunc.contorl.maybe.Maybe<A>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public abstract class Maybe<A>
extends Object
implements Hkt<Maybe.μ,A>, Monad<Maybe.μ,A>, Case2<Maybe<A>,Maybe.None<A>,Maybe.Just<A>>
    Represents a value of something(Just) or a value of Nothing.
